args: cond:Bool a:Int b:Int c:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: A bound condition reused around arithmetic must be equivalent to direct use of the original condition.
law: (= (with [flag {cond}] (fuzz-add (if flag {a} {b}) (if flag {c} {a}))) (fuzz-add (if {cond} {a} {b}) (if {cond} {c} {a})))
